  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of EPI-743 in Children With Leigh Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2B Randomized, Placebo Controlled, Double Blind Clinical Trial of EPI-743 in Children With Leigh Syndrome</official_title>
